## üß™ Test Program: GoCV

Create a `main.go`:

```go
package main

import (
    "gocv.io/x/gocv"
)

func main() {
    webcam, _ := gocv.VideoCaptureDevice(0)
    window := gocv.NewWindow("Webcam")
    img := gocv.NewMat()
    for {
        webcam.Read(&img)
        window.IMShow(img)
        if window.WaitKey(1) >= 0 {
            break
        }
    }
}
```

Then run:

```bash
go run main.go
```

